== Configuration ==

Make dash the default system shell:

{{RootCmd
|cd /bin
|ln -sf dash sh
|echo /bin/dash >>/etc/shells
|usermod -s /bin/dash root
}}

Use dash as current shell:

{{Cmd|chsh -s /bin/dash}}

